data.description:
Cute 3 bedroom 1 3/4 bath home on large Clearwood lot. This home is located on a cul-de-sac with an out-building for extra storage. Clearwood has miles of walking / hiking trails, swimming pool and spa and many sport courts for added fun. Partially fenced yard.
Application $45 per adult, security deposit $1150, Rent $1295 per month, one small dog allowed with approval and security deposit.
